        "message": "执行子工作空间备份（两个子目录分别推送到不同 branch）：\n\n步骤1 - planner:\n1. cd ~/.openclaw/workspaces/feishu-planner\n2. git add -A\n3. git commit -m \"Weekly subworkspace backup $(date +%Y-%m-%d)\"（无变化则跳过）\n4. git push origin planner\n\n步骤2 - moltbook:\n1. cd ~/.openclaw/workspaces/feishu-moltbook\n2. git add -A\n3. git commit -m \"Weekly subworkspace backup $(date +%Y-%m-%d)\"（无变化则跳过）\n4. git push origin moltbook\n\n两个都成功则回复 HEARTBEAT_OK。任一失败则报告错误。",
